title: Week 9 NFL Picks Against the Spread, Trent Green, Bryant McFadden (Football 11/02)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Bryant McFadden to break down the Thursday night game and the incredible performance by Nick Mullens. The guys debate if the Raiders quit, if Oakland is the worst team in football and then talk about B Mac's new podcast. Then Trent Green of the NFL on CBS joins the show to break down Chiefs-Browns and whether Patrick Mahomes can keep up his torrid pace. Finally, Pete Prisco and R.J. White come on to make picks for every single game against the spread in Week 9.
This episode is sponsored by www.ZipRecruiter.com
